metadata.title: Alaska Interim Land Cover Mapping

creators.name: U.S. Geological Survey (USGS), EROS Data Center, Alaska Field Office

metadata.description: Data Type: Vegetation/Land Cover/Soils;  Statewide landcover mapping effort to produce regional scale landcover mapping over the entire state using Landsat satellite data. This project integrated a variety of landcover mapping efforts conducted by a variety of state and federal agencies for a variety of resource inventory projects. Mapping classifications were crosswalked in attempts to standardize land mapping units.
